			"value": "<p><strong>Granted By</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.monster-homebrewery.creatures.Actor.Yo98ERYF6Dn0lQ7j.Item.EuKTCkMN0rIlr722]</p><hr /><p>The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{confused }for 1 minute.</p><p>While confused, the creature gains the following effects:</p><ul><li><p>The creature deals 2 additional damage on melee Strikes. This additional damage is halved if the creature's weapon or unarmed attack is agile.</p></li><li><p>The creature can't use action with the concentrate trait unless they also have the rage trait. The creature can stille @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.BlAOM2X92SI6HMtJ]{Seek} while raging.</p></li></ul>",
